%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%20Rajya%20Was%20No%20Hindu%20Raj%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmahatma-gandhi-angel-of-history-ram-rajya-ayodhya%5C%22%3Elot%20of%20talk%20about%20Ram%20Rajya%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20even%20as%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20is%20being%20chanted%20by%20thugs%20unleashing%20violence%20against%20mosques%2C%20churches%20and%20Indians%20following%20Islam%20and%20Christianity.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20last%20words%20when%20shot%20at%20by%20a%20Hindu%20fanatic%20on%20this%20day%20in%201948%20were%20%E2%80%98Hey%20Ram%E2%80%99%20and%20he%20would%20have%20reacted%20the%20same%20way%20at%20what%20is%20happening%20today%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogan%20so%20aggressively%20and%20menacingly%20recited%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20it%20is%20instructive%20to%20recall%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20advice%20about%20such%20slogans.%20In%20an%20article%20written%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHarijan%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20August%209%2C%201942%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20letter%20he%20received%20from%20someone%20who%20informed%20him%20that%20members%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayam%20Sevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20in%20their%20morning%20rallies%20were%20reciting%20slogans%20against%20Muslims.%20Gandhi%20wrote%20about%203%2C000%20members%20of%20RSS%20organising%20a%20daily%20lathi%20drill%20followed%20by%20reciting%20the%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9CHindustan%20belongs%20to%20Hindus%20and%20to%20nobody%20else.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20referred%20to%20the%C2%A0%20brief%20discourse%20accompanying%20those%20menacing%20utterances.%20During%20the%20discourse%20the%20speakers%20used%20to%20say%3A%20%E2%80%9CDrive%20out%20the%20English%20first%20and%20then%20we%20shall%20subjugate%20the%20Muslims.%20If%20they%20do%20not%20listen%2C%20we%20shall%20kill%20them.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CTaking%20the%20evidence%20at%20its%20face%20value%E2%80%9D%2C%20Gandhi%20sharply%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20slogan%20is%20wrong%20and%20the%20central%20theme%20of%20the%20discourse%20is%20worse%E2%80%9D.%20Stating%20that%20%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.belongs%20to%20Parsis%2C%20Beni%20Israels%2C%20to%20Indian%20Christians%2C%20Muslims%20and%20other%20non-Hindus%20as%20much%20as%20to%20Hindus%E2%80%9D%2C%20Gandhi%20firmly%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20an%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0anchored%20in%20any%20one%20faith%20and%20categorically%20affirmed%2C%20%E2%80%9CFree%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0will%20be%20no%20Hindu%20raj%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Indian%20raj%20based%20not%20on%20the%20majority%20of%20any%20religious%20sect%20or%20community%20but%20on%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20whole%20people%20without%20distinction%20of%20religion%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20appealed%20to%20the%20lathi%20wielding%20RSS%20activists%20to%20avoid%20reciting%20such%20violent%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20observing%20the%20solemn%C2%A0%20occasion%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20martyrdom%20day%20on%2030%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%C2%A0January%202024%20we%20need%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20those%20words%20which%20are%20more%20relevant%20in%20the%20present%20day%20when%20the%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogan%20is%20being%20used%20against%20others%20pursuing%20faiths%20different%20from%20those%20of%20the%20majority%20community%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Bhopal%20on%2010%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%C2%A0September%201929%2C%20Gandhi%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20his%20idea%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20was%20not%20theocratic%20in%20nature%20and%20scope%C2%A0%20and%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%98By%20Ramarajya%E2%80%99%20I%20do%20not%20mean%20Hindu%20Raj%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CI%20mean%20by%20%E2%80%98Ramarajya%E2%80%99%20the%20Divine%20Raj%2C%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God%E2%80%A6%20For%20me%20Rama%20and%20Rahim%20are%20one%20and%20the%20same%20deity%E2%80%9D.%20Rahim%2C%20or%20the%20merciful%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20synonyms%20of%20Allah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20acknowledge%20no%20other%20god%20but%20the%20one%20god%20of%20Truth%20and%20righteousness%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWhether%20the%20Rama%20of%20my%20imagination%20ever%20lived%20or%20not%20on%20this%20earth%2C%20the%20ancient%20ideal%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20is%20undoubtedly%20one%20of%20true%20democracy%20in%20which%20the%20meanest%20citizen%20could%20be%20sure%20of%20swift%20justice%20without%20an%20elaborate%20and%20costly%20procedure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20pluralistic%20nature%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20stands%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20shouting%20for%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20by%20several%20of%20those%20who%20attended%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20organised%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftheologically-determined-politics-weakens-representative-government%5C%22%3ETheologically%20Determined%20Politics%20Weakens%20Representative%20Government%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20idea%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20was%20rejected%20by%20Gandhi%20as%20early%20as%201929%20and%20it%20is%20tragic%20that%20in%20a%20meeting%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20this%20divisive%20slogan%20was%20raised%20and%20none%20of%20the%20leaders%20attending%20that%20event%20even%20raised%20any%20objections%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERam%20Rajya%20and%20Freedom%20of%20Press%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20defined%20Ram%20Rajya%20from%20multiple%20perspectives%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20the%20exercise%20of%20power%20in%20a%20regulated%20manner.%20Writing%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENavajivan%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20October%2020%2C%201929%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20statement%20of%20a%20young%20man%20that%20%3Cem%3Eswaraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20meant%20the%20transfer%20of%20power%20from%20British%20hands%20to%20Indian%20hands%C2%A0%20and%20that%20it%C2%A0%20meant%20regulated%20power%20in%20the%20hands%20of%2030%20crore%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20there%20is%20such%20rule%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed%2C%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20a%20young%20girl%20will%20feel%20herself%20safe%20and%2C%20if%20the%20imagination%20of%20a%20poet%20is%20correct%2C%20animals%20like%20dogs%2C%20etc.%2C%20who%20live%20among%20human%20beings%20will%20have%20a%20similar%20feeling%20of%20safety%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20explained%20that%20several%20basic%20decisions%20in%20regard%20to%20swaraj%20would%20not%20be%C2%A0%20subject%20to%20officials%20in%20power%20but%20would%20be%C2%A0%20based%20on%20truth%20and%20justice.%20Gandhi%20remarked%20that%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20succinctly%20called%20this%20kind%20of%20swaraj%20%E2%80%98Ramarajya%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20added%20that%20in%20case%C2%A0%20the%20Muslims%20and%20others%20misinterpret%20it%2C%20such%20a%20Raj%20could%20be%20called%20the%20rule%20of%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20talk%20of%20ushering%20in%20Ram%20Rajya%20following%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20should%20note%20that%20the%20institutions%20which%20regulate%20the%20power%20of%20the%20executive%20under%20their%20control%20have%20been%20considerably%20weakened%20to%20create%20conditions%20for%20the%20exercise%20of%20unregulated%20power%20%E2%80%93%20which%20negates%20the%20idea%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20contemplated%20by%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20two%20years%20before%20the%20attainment%20of%20independence%2C%20Gandhi%20outlined%20the%20religious%20and%20political%20dimensions%20of%20Ram%20Rajya.%20When%20one%20Sailendra%20Nath%20Chattopadhyaya%20asked%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20you%20wish%20to%20live%20for%20125%20years%2C%20and%20what%20is%20Ram%20Rajya%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20explained%20that%20his%C2%A0wish%20to%20live%20for%20125%20years%20depended%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20selfless%20service%20he%20would%20render.%20On%20the%20issue%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20he%20explained%20that%20when%C2%A0%20religiously%20translated%20this%20meant%C2%A0%20Kingdom%20of%20God%20on%20Earth%20but%20its%20political%20components%20were%20%E2%80%9Cperfect%20democracy%20in%20which%20inequalities%20based%20on%20possession%20and%20non-possession%2C%20colour%2C%20race%20or%20creed%20or%20sex%20vanish.%E2%80%9D%20He%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20in%20such%20a%20Ram%20Rajya%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6land%20and%20State%20belong%20to%20the%20people%2C%20justice%20is%20prompt%2C%20perfect%20and%20cheap%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20there%20is%20freedom%20of%20worship%2C%20speech%20and%20the%20Press.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20conception%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20terms%20of%20political%20attributes%20such%20as%20freedom%20of%20press%20should%20prompt%C2%A0our%20rulers%20to%20re-evaluate%20their%20actions%20because%20of%20which%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0ranks%20161%3Csup%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fsup%3Ein%20the%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20Ram%20Rajya%20was%20conceived%20as%20reign%20of%20the%20self-imposed%20law%20of%20moral%20restraint.%20A%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20impunity%20and%20majoritarianism%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20%3Cspan%3ESahu%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20