IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecardiovascular%20disease%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20previously%20clean%20bill%20of%20health%2C%20the%20doctor%20said%20that%20nothing%20seemed%20particularly%20concerning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%2C%20you're%20young%2C%20you're%20healthy%2C%20there's%20nothing%20in%20your%20history%2C%20let's%20just%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20symptoms.%20So%20I%20left%20that%20appointment%20with%20no%20answers%2C%26quot%3B%20Dancy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20she%20visited%20a%20second%20doctor%20who%20said%20she%20probably%20had%20a%20virus%20and%20should%20just%20wait%20for%20it%20to%20pass%2C%20but%20her%20symptoms%20kept%20getting%20worse.%20Her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fhow-to-get-rid-of-sore-muscles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emuscles%20were%20so%20fatigued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20couldn't%20walk%20to%20the%20bathroom%20just%20a%20few%20feet%20away%2C%20and%20her%20chest%20felt%20so%20congested%20that%20she%20couldn't%20lie%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20struggling.%20I%20was%20dragging%20my%20body%20around.%20I%20was%20extremely%20tired%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20suffocating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUndiagnosed%20heart%20failure%20made%20her%20feel%20like%20she%20was%20dying%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20simply%20couldn't%20take%20the%20symptoms%20anymore%2C%20Dancy%20took%20herself%20to%20the%20ER%2C%20where%20she%20was%20misdiagnosed%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fhow-do-you-get-pneumonia%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epneumonia%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20fluid%20was%20found%20in%20her%20lungs.%20But%20taking%20the%20antibiotics%20and%20inhaler%20doctors%20prescribed%20just%20seemed%20to%20make%20things%20worse%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20started%20the%20treatment%20of%20pneumonia%2C%20I%20really%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20dying.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20death%20felt%20like.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20really%20being%20ill%20felt%20like%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20is%20not%20getting%20better%2C%20and%20I%20shouldn't%20feel%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Dancy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20stage%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20the%20ER%2C%20for%20her%20fourth%20medical%20visit%2C%20and%20was%20finally%20diagnosed%20with%20peripartum%20cardiomyopathy%2C%20a%20rare%20form%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-signs-of-heart-failure-from-nurse-who-missed-arrhythmia-2022-12%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eheart%20failure%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20happens%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20pregnancy%20or%20in%20the%20months%20after%20birth.%20She%20was%2035%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20her%20diagnosis%2C%20Dancy%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20out%20that%20she%20had%20such%20a%20serious%20health%20condition%20because%20she%20wasn't%20aware%20that%20heart%20disease%20could%20affect%20younger%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20also%20felt%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-who-has-been-gaslighted-shares-advice-for-patients-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoctors%20dismissed%20her%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20she%20was%20young%20and%20seemingly%20healthy.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20personally%2C%20I%20did%20feel%20that%20I%20wasn't%20heard%2C%20but%20I'd%20also%20played%20a%20part%20in%20that.%20Not%20going%20in%20there%20prepared%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECardiovascular%20disease%20kills%20more%20women%20in%20the%20US%20than%20any%20other%20condition%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECardiovascular%20disease%2C%20which%20is%20the%20umbrella%20term%20for%20conditions%20that%20affect%20your%20heart%20or%20circulation%2C%20is%20the%20number%20one%20killer%20of%20women%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20causing%20one%20in%20three%20deaths%20each%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Heart%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeart%20failure%20is%20one%20type%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-factors-that-may-increase-your-risk-for-heart-disease-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECVD%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20the%20heart%20doesn't%20pump%20properly%2C%20usually%20because%20it%20has%20become%20too%20weak%20or%20stiff.%20This%20means%20it's%20not%20meeting%20the%20body's%20need%20for%20blood%20and%20oxygen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeart%20failure%20typically%20occurs%20as%20a%20result%20of%20another%20health%20condition%2C%20such%20as%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20coronary%20heart%20disease%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2Fhypertension%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20blood%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20heart%20rhythm%20and%20valve%20abnormalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmoking%2C%20being%20overweight%2C%20eating%20foods%20high%20in%20fat%20and%20cholesterol%2C%20and%20living%20a%20sedentary%20lifestyle%20can%20contribute%20to%20heart%20failure%20because%20they%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20developing%20heart%20conditions%20associated%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeripartum%20cardiomyopathy%20is%20diagnosed%20in%20one%20in%20every%201%2C000%20to%20one%20in%20every%204%2C000%20deliveries%2C%20but%20cases%20appear%20to%20be%20rising%2C%20according%20to%20the%20AHA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20being%20pregnant%2C%20there%20is%20no%20known%20cause%20of%20peripartum%20cardiomyopathy%2C%20but%20risk%20factors%20include%20being%20obese%2C%20having%20a%20poor%20diet%2C%20smoking%2C%20old%20age%2C%20multiple%20pregnancies%2C%20and%20being%20of%20African%20American%20descent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222201%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marian%20Dancy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20