0imposed%20restrictions%20on%20the%20highlands%20in%20the%20Kakjung%20area%20of%20Ladakh%20which%20have%20been%20traditionally%20used%20by%20the%20tribal%20people%20for%20grazing%20their%20livestock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disclosure%20comes%20days%20after%20Ladakhi%20tribesmen%20and%20the%20Chinese%20army%20personnel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fladakh-local-herders-clash-with-chinese-solders-over-access-to-grazing-land%5C%22%3Eclashed%20at%20Patrolling%20Point%2035%2C%2036%20and%2037%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kakjung%20area%20of%20Chushul%20sector%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20increasing%20tensions%20following%20the%202020%20Galwan%20Valley%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshey%20Spalzang%2C%20the%20in-charge%20councillor%20of%20Nyoma%20constituency%20of%20Ladakh%20where%20the%20clash%20took%20place%20on%20January%202%2C%20said%20that%20the%20herdsmen%20involved%20in%20the%20clash%20have%20been%20reportedly%20ordered%20by%20PLA%20soldiers%20to%20keep%20their%20livestock%20away%20from%20some%20parts%20of%20Kakjung%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Chinese%20forces%20have%20pushed%20the%20boundary%20further%20downwards%20and%20the%20herdsmen%20have%20been%20asked%20not%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20areas%20which%20were%20traditionally%20used%20as%20a%20grazing%20ground.%20They%20(PLA)%20are%20claiming%20the%20area%20as%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20Spalzang%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20animals%20know%20about%20the%20border%20when%20there%20is%20no%20fence!%20The%20area%20is%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%20We%20have%20asked%20the%20administration%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20PLA%20so%20that%20our%20herdsmen%20can%20continue%20grazing%20their%20livestock%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20a%20meeting%20was%20held%20by%20the%20Army%20and%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20civil%20administration%20on%20January%2013%20where%20the%20face-off%20between%20the%20herdsmen%20and%20Chinese%20forces%20was%20discussed%20and%20several%20security%20measures%20were%20proposed%20for%20ensuring%20that%20the%20herdsmen%20don%E2%80%99t%20lose%20access%20to%20their%20traditional%20pastures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20herdsmen%20have%20been%20assured%20that%20the%20Army%20and%20Indo-Tibetan%20Police%20Force%20personnel%20will%20accompany%20them%20and%20provide%20them%20protection%20in%20case%20such%20incidents%20happen%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20administration%20is%20committed%20to%20protecting%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Army%20has%20not%20officially%20reacted%20to%20the%20clash%20in%20Kakjung%2C%20its%20Ladakh-based%20Fire%20and%20Fury%20Corps%20shared%20on%20Twitter%20a%20few%20adulatory%20posts%20of%20Konchok%20Stanzin%2C%20councillor%20of%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20Chushul%20constituency%2C%20who%20lauded%20the%20Army%20for%20facilitating%20herdsmen%20in%20the%20highlands%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fire%20and%20Fury%20Corps%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20post%20of%20Stanzin%20which%20showed%20a%20shepherd%20saluting%20the%20cameraperson%20while%20expressing%20gratitude%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20getting%20all%20the%20help%20from%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20Thank%20you%20Indian%20Army.%20Bharat%20Mata%20Ki%20Jai%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tashi%20Namgail%2C%20the%20shepherd%2C%20is%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%2017-second%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20cornered%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20the%20clash%20in%20Kakjung%2C%20with%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20stating%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cexposed%20the%20hollowness%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20which%20has%20been%20allegedly%20complicit%20in%20attempting%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccover%20up%20the%20worst%20territorial%20setback%20in%20six%20decades%20for%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShot%20in%20January%202024%2C%20the%20video%20shows%20PLA%20troops%20accompanied%20by%20an%20armoured%20vehicle%20harassing%20and%20blocking%20shepherds%E2%80%99%20access%20to%20grazing%20areas%20near%20Patrolling%20Points%2035%20and%2036%20in%20the%20Chushul%20sector%20that%20lie%20well%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20claim%20line.%20Indian%20authorities%20have%20reportedly%20asked%20the%20shepherds%20not%20to%20return%20to%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20Ladakh%20has%20a%20population%20of%205.69%20lakh%20goats%20and%20sheep%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20raised%20on%20the%20pastures%20in%20the%20highlands%20of%20the%20arid%20desert%20region.%20These%20includes%20the%20famed%20Changthangi%20goats%20whose%20wool%20is%20processed%20to%20make%20the%20famed%20Kashmiri%20Pashmina%20shawl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENyoma%20councillor%20Spalzang%20said%20that%20the%20Kakjung%20area%20hosts%20about%2070%2C000%20goats%20and%20sheep%20for%20two%20months%20during%20the%20grazing%20period%2C%20which%20starts%20in%20November%20or%20December%2C%20after%20which%20the%20tribal%20families%20associated%20with%20the%20trade%20start%20their%20downward%20migration%20towards%20the%20areas%20in%20the%20plains%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20similar%20incident%20had%20happened%20earlier%20also%20in%20Kakjung%20Valley.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20administration%20had%20facilitated%20the%20tribal%20families%20by%20setting%20up%20two%20stone%20shelters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Chinese%20forces%20have%20been%20raising%20objections%20to%20these%20structures.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20restrictions%20directly%20impact%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20herdsmen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Spalzang%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20in%20Kakjung%20took%20place%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20border%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20South%20Asian%20giants%20have%20failed%20to%20make%20any%20significant%20breakthrough.%20Indo-China%20bilateral%20relations%20are%20on%20a%20downward%20spiral%20as%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20proximity%20with%20Washington%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20deadly%20Galwan%20Valley%20clashes%20in%20Ladakh%20in%202020%2C%20India%20and%20China%20have%20been%20holding%20bilateral%20talks%20at%20the%20military%20level%20to%20resolve%20the%20dispute%20along%20the%20tense%20border.%20In%20his%20statement%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20Ramesh%20alleged%20that%20Chinese%20troops%20%E2%80%9Ccontinue%20to%20deny%20Indian%20patrols%20access%20to%20the%20strategic%20Depsang%20Plains%2C%20Demchok%20and%20other%20areas%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChina%20continues%20to%20deny%20us%20access%20to%202%2C000%20square%20km%20despite%2018%20rounds%20of%20military%20talks%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Chinese%20forces%20objected%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20Ladakhi%20herdsmen%20at%20the%20Demchok%20sector%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20perception%20of%20the%20LAC%2C%20which%20was%20followed%20by%20meetings%20between%20the%20commanders%20of%20the%20two%20armies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706787012000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01164821%2FGFGBD9lXcAAfLGm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fladakh-chinas-pla-imposes-restrictions-on-where-tribal-people-can-graze-livestock%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Herdsmen%20involved%20in%20the%20January%202%20clash%20with%20the%20PLA%20have%20been%20reportedly%20ordered%20by%20PLA%20soldiers%20to%20keep%20their%20livestock%20away%20from%20some%20parts%20of%20Kakjung%20Valley.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fladakh-chinas-pla-imposes-restrictions-on-where-tribal-people-can-graze-livestock%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2