Cn%E2%80%94%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20(%40yadavakhilesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyadavakhilesh%2Fstatus%2F1752946962125795360%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister%20underlined%20that%20the%20government%20is%20working%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20country%20by%202047%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20works%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20'reform%2C%20perform%2C%20and%20transform'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20budget%20is%20to%20meet%20the%20central%20government's%20essential%20expenditure%20for%20the%20first%20four%20months%20of%20the%20new%20fiscal%20year%20that%20starts%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Modi%20government%20presented%20its%20last%20budget.%20Want%20to%20thank%20the%20finance%20minister%20because%20she%20did%20it%20with%20a%20very%20heavy%20heart%20and%20presented%20the%20last%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20addressing%20party%20workers%20in%20Raigad%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Chaturvedi%2C%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%2C%20taking%20her%20cue%20from%20the%20cold%20weather%20said%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20poured%20%26quot%3Bcold%20water%26quot%3B%20on%20people's%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20can%20say%20is%20that%20in%20this%20cold%20weather%2C%20what%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20has%20done%2C%20she%20has%20poured%20cold%20water%20over%20the%20expectations%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%2C%20leader%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20a%20televised%20address%20following%20the%20budget%2C%20said%20it%20will%20empower%20the%20four%20pillars%20of%20developed%20India%2C%20namely%20the%20young%2C%20poor%2C%20women%20and%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20budget%20of%20creating%20India's%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20young%20aspirations%20of%20a%20young%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20Congress'%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20said%20the%20budget%20only%20aims%20to%20woo%20people%20ahead%20of%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20a%20budget%20to%20provide%20employment%20to%20the%20unemployed...%20This%20budget%20is%20nothing%20but%20to%20woo%20people%20in%20this%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chowdhury.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Finance%20Minister%20took%20a%20long%20time%20to%20hail%20praises%20but%20delivery%20was%20zero.%20They%20are%20going%20to%20present%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20previous%20government...%20Nothing%20much%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20country%20are%20already%20disappointed.%20Moreover%2C%20you%20realise%20that%20performance%20incentives%20are%20given%20to%20the%20bridge%20companies%2C%20and%20not%20going%20to%20the%20deserving%20ones.%20People%20are%20rejected%20with%20this%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DMK%20MP%20Dayanidhi%20Maran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMere%20administrative%20exercise%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20the%20requisite%20funds%20to%20carry%20on%20its%20normal%20business%20until%20the%20new%20parliament%20is%20constituted%20and%20a%20new%20government%20is%20formed.%20And%20that's%20what%20they%20have%20done%2C%20except%20for%20making%20their%20obligatory%20self-congratulatory%2C%20self-praise%20phrases%2C%20nothing%20else%20is%20there%20and%20nothing%20should%20have%20been%20there%2C%20and%20rightly%20so.%20Nothing%20is%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress%20MP%20Karti%20Chidambaram.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706776140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fu1706ego_nirmala-_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw