https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fexclusive-shark-tank-india-3s-ai-based-cooking-appliance-pitcher-mehak-mody-on-not-striking-a-deal-though-we-denied-peyush-bansals-offer-we-resonated-on-technology%2Farticleshow%2F107320350.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20Foreigners%20And%20A%20Sophisticated%20Drug%20Lab%20At%20%26quot%3BLuxury%26quot%3B%20Home%20Near%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFour%20foreign%20nationals%20and%20a%20luxurious%20house%20near%20Delhi%20-%20a%20detail%20that%20didn't%20mean%20much%20to%20anyone%20until%20it%20was%20known%20that%20the%20team%20of%20four%20was%20using%20the%20property%20to%20produce%20%26quot%3Bfine-quality%26quot%3B%20banned%20methamphetamine%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lab%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bluxurious%20and%20lonely%20private%20place%26quot%3B%20at%20Alestonia%20Estate%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Greater%20Noida%20was%20busted%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20police%20recovered%20445%20grams%20of%20fine-quality%20banned%20methamphetamine%20drug%20and%2020.5%20kg%20of%20raw%20materials%20that%20included%20one%20kg%20of%20pseudoephedrine%20-%20an%20ingredient%20for%20the%20illicit%20manufacture%20of%20methamphetamines.%20Sophisticated%20equipment%2C%20including%20a%20heating%20mantle%20machine%20and%20high-quality%20face%20masks%2C%20were%20also%20recovered%20from%20the%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENigerian%20national%20Eze%20Uchenna%20James%20(49)%2C%20Alitumo%20Ifedi%20Shedrack%20(28)%2C%20Eze%20Ibe%20Emeka%20Chibuzo%20alias%20Iko%20(56)%20and%20Kenyan%20national%20Ivo%20Osita%20alias%20Usta%20alias%20Osey%20(44)%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Eze%2C%20Alitumo%20and%20Ivo%20were%20previously%20arrested%20and%20convicted%20in%20drug%20trafficking%20cases%20and%20were%20out%20on%20conditional%20bail%2C%20according%20to%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Pol