%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Fbudget-2024-here-s-what-fm-nirmala-sitharaman-said-about-income-tax-124020100408_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Fbudget-2024-here-s-what-fm-nirmala-sitharaman-said-about-income-tax-124020100408_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Fbudget-2024-here-s-what-fm-nirmala-sitharaman-said-about-income-tax-124020100408_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Last%20Budget%20Before%20Elections%2C%20A%20Ram%20Mandir%20Mention%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Interim%20Budget%20for%202024%2C%20being%20presented%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20also%20saw%20a%20mention%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Listing%20out%20the%20expected%20benefits%20of%20the%20rooftop%20solarisation%20programme%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20scheme%20is%20being%20implemented%20following%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20%26quot%3Bresolve%26quot%3B%20to%20do%20so%20after%20the%20historic%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20to%20New%20Delhi%20from%20Ayodhya%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20indicated%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20realisation%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20devotees%20of%20the%20world%20get%20energy%20from%20the%20light%20of%20Suryavanshi%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20decision%20I%20have%20taken%20after%20returning%20from%20Ayodhya%20is%20that%20our%20government%20will%20launch%20'Pradhanmantri%20Suryodaya%20Yojana'%20with%20the%20target%20of%20installing%20rooftop%20solar%20on%201%20crore%20houses.%20This%20will%20not%20only%20reduce%20the%20electricity%20bill%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20middle%20class%2C%20but%20also%20make%20India%20self-reliant%20in%20the%20field%20of%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20her%20sixth%20straight%20Budget%20speech%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThrough%20rooftop%20solarisation%2C%20one%20crore%20households%20will%20be%20enabled%20to%20obtain%20up%20to%20300%20units%20free%20electricity%20every%20month.%20This%20scheme%20follows%20the%20resolve%20of%20the%20Honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20the%20historic%20day%20of%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20minister%20said%20the%20scheme%20is%20not%20only%20expected%20to%20result%20in%20savings%20for%20households%2C%20but%20also%20generate%20entrepreneurship%20and%20employment%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20details%2C%20she%20said%20households%20can%20save%20up%20to%20Rs%2018%2C000%20a%20year%20from%20free%20solar%20electricity%20as%20well%20as%20selling%20the%20surplus%20to%20the%20distribution%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%2C%20apart%20from%20facilitating%20the%20charging%20of%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20the%20scheme%20will%20produce%20entrepreneurship%20opportunities%20for%20a%20large%20number%20of%20vendors%2C%20who%20will%20be%20engaged%20in%20supply%20and%20installation%20of%20equipment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployment%20opportunities%2C%20she%20pointed%20out%2C%20will%20also%20be%20generated%20for%20youth%20with%20technical%20skills%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20installation%20and%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706772960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fvdeicmj8_ram-mandir-_625x300_23_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fin-last-budget-before-elections-a-ram-mandir-mention-4972394%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Interim%20Budget%20for%202024%2C%20being%20presented%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20also%20saw%20a%20mention%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fin-last-budget-before-elections-a-ram-mandir-mention-4972394%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fin-last-budget-before-elections-a-ram-mandir-mention-4972394%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fin-last-budget-before-elections-a-ram-mandir-mention-4972394%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%202024%3A%20Some%20relief%20for%20taxpayers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706772604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107318870%2Cimgsize-46020.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbudget%2Fbudget-2024-income-tax-some-relief-for-taxpayers-outstanding-personal-tax-demands-up-to-rs-25000-withdrawn%2Farticleshow%2F107318865.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%20Budget%202024%20speech%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20announced%20the%20removal%20of%20disputed%20direct%20tax%20demands%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20benefiting%20approximately%201%20crore%20taxpayers.%20The%20proposal%20aims%20to%20address%20unresolved%20tax%20demands%20from%20FY%202009-10%20and%20FY%202010-11%20to%202014-15.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbudget%2Fbudget-2024-income-tax-some-relief-for-taxpayers-outstanding-personal-tax-demands-up-to-rs-25000-withdrawn%2Farticleshow%2F107318865.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Tax%20Change%2C%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Bharat%26quot%3B%20Mantra%20In%20Last%20Budget%20Before%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20no%20change%20to%20income%20tax%20slabs%2C%20which%20have%20been%20reduced%20and%20rationalised%2C%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Finterim-budget-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20interim%20Budget%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnirmala-sitharaman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20as%20she%20read%20out%20a%20statement%20of%20the%20country's%20finances%20in%20a%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament.%20%26quot%3BI%20propose%20to%20retain%20the%20same%20tax%20rates%20for%20direct%20and%20indirect%20taxes%2C%20including%20import%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20did%2C%20though%2C%20propose%20to%20withdraw%20outstanding%20direct%20tax%20demands%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%2C000%20till%20FY09%2F10%20and%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20FY10%2F11%20to%2014%2F15%2C%20and%20said%20it%20would%20benefit%20around%20one%20crore%20taxpayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20count%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20there%20are%20a%20large%20number%20of%20petty%2C%20non-verified%2C%20non-reconciled%2C%20or%20disputed%2C%20direct%20tax%20demands%2C%20many%20dating%20to%201962%2C%20which%20remain%20on%20the%20books%2C%20causing%20anxiety%20to%20honest%20taxpayers...%20I%20propose%20to%20withdraw%20such%20outstanding%20direct%20tax%20demands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Finterim-budget-2024-direct-tax-demand-up-to-rs-25-000-to-be-withdrawn-see-key-details-4972136%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_bigstory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDirect%20Tax%20Demand%20Up%20To%20%E2%82%B925%2C000%20To%20Be%20Withdrawn.%20See%20Key%20Details%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20overall%20tax%20picture%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20said%20direct%20collections%20had%20more%20than%20trebled%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20people%20filing%20returns%20had%20increased%202.4%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hold%20on%20revisions%20to%20tax%20slabs%20was%20not%20unexpected%20given%20this%20is%20an%20interim%20budget%20-%20essentially%20to%20keep%20the%20government%20running%20till%20a%20new%20administration%20is%20elected%20and%20takes%20charge%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20LIVE%20COVERAGE%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-budget-2024-live-updates-budget-2024-interim-budget-budget-nirmala-sitharaman-finance-minister-fm-income-tax-slab-income-tax-new-regime-income-t-4970811%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman's%202024%20Interim%20Budget%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20full%20Union%20Budget%20will%20likely%20be%20presented%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20that%20tax%20slabs%20will%20stay%20the%20same%20will%20disappoint%20salaried%20taxpayers%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20had%20been%20hoping%20for%20cuts%20to%20help%20deal%20with%20perennial%20cost-of-living%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20significant%20point%20for%20taxpayers%20is%20that%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20both%20the%20old%20and%20new%20tax%20regimes%20will%20continue%2C%20meaning%20people%20can%20choose%20between%20them%20when%20filing%20their%20returns.%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20also%20touched%20on%20the%20introduction%20of%20new%20forms%20and%20software%20to%20make%20filing%20easier%20and%20simpler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Finterim-budget-2024-huge-investments-for-lakshadweep-to-draw-tourists-nirmala-sitharaman-4972065%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuge%20Investments%20For%20Lakshadweep%20To%20Draw%20Tourists%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20processing%20time%20of%20tax%20returns%20have%20been%20reduced%20from%2093%20days%20in%202014%20to%20just%2010%20days%20this%20year%2C%20thereby%20making%20refunds%20faster%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cem%3EViksit%20%3C%2Fem%3EBharat%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresenting%20her%20sixth%20straight%20(but%20first%20interim)%20budget%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20also%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20is%20working%20to%20make%20India%20a%20'%3Cem%3EViksit%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Developed)%20Bharat'%20by%202047%2C%20and%20that%20this%20development%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ball%20round%2C%20all%20inclusive%2C%20and%20all%20pervasive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20vision%20for%20%3Cem%3EViksit%20%3C%2Fem%3EBharat%20is%20that%20of%20a%20prosperous%20Bharat...%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature%20and%20modern%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20providing%20opportunities%20for%20all%20to%20reach%20their%20potential.%20The%20next%20five%20years%20will%20see%20unprecedented%20development%20and%20golden%20moments%20to%20realise%20the%20goal%20of%20a%20developed%20India...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fin-last-budget-before-elections-a-ram-mandir-mention-4972394%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20Last%20Budget%20Before%20Elections%2C%20A%20Ram%20Mandir%20Mention%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20government%20plans%20to%20form%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh-powered%20committee%26quot%3B%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bextensive%20consideration%20of%20challenges%20arising%20from%20fast%20population%20growth%20and%20demographic%20challenges%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20will%20be%20mandated%20to%20make%20recommendations%20to%20address%20these%20challenges%20comprehensively%2C%20in%20relation%20to%20t