umstances.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20committee%20responsible%20for%20regulating%20lectures%20at%20the%20IIT%20Bombay%20campus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-lecture-by-gn-devy-101706641203094.html%5C%22%3Emade%20the%20decision%20to%20call%20off%20the%20lecture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20very%20excited%20to%20hear%20Professor%20Devy%20as%20he%20is%20an%20intellectual%20personality%20who%20delivers%20his%20thoughts%20on%20history%20and%20present%20society.%20We%20were%20very%20happy%20when%20the%20institute%20decided%20to%20invite%20him%20to%20the%20campus.%20But%20going%20by%20past%20instances%2C%20we%20feared%20that%20the%20institute%20may%20cancel%20the%20lecture%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-lecture-by-gn-devy-101706641203094.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20student%20from%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-conference-left-education-ministry%5C%22%3E%20IIT%20Bombay%20Cancels%20Conference%20on%20Left%20Movement%20After%20%E2%80%98Call%20From%20Senior%20Official%E2%80%99%20in%20Edu%20Ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Devy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fiit-bombay-cancels-lecture-by-gn-devy-101706641203094.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20never%20been%20previously%20associated%20with%20IIT%20Bombay.%20A%20professor%20from%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20lecture%20committee%20invited%20me%20to%20give%20a%20lecture.%20But%20a%20day%20before%20I%20was%20leaving%2C%20the%20same%20person%20called%20to%20inform%20me%20about%20cancellation%20of%20the%20lecture.%20I%20did%20not%20even%20bother%20to%20ask%20the%20reason%20as%20it%20is%20not%20my%20basic%20ri