h%20ensures%20that%20students%20with%20low%20vision%20can%20readily%20identify%20and%20locate%20important%20elements%2C%20such%20as%20the%20switchboard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmell%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20to%20make%20the%20classrooms%20even%20more%20distinctive%20from%20each%20other%2C%20the%20architect%20decided%20to%20engage%20the%20sense%20of%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20planted%20aromatic%20plants%20at%20entries%2C%20which%20can%20assist%20students%20in%20marking%20and%20identifying%20places.%20These%20elements%20serve%20as%20different%20clues%20incorporated%20into%20our%20design.%20Students%2C%20based%20on%20their%20comfort%20and%20understanding%2C%20use%20these%20clues%20to%20navigate%20the%20building.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20has%20brightly%20coloured%20doors%20to%20help%20the%20students%20with%20partial%20vision%20navigate%20better.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340124%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20has%20brightly%20coloured%20doors%20to%20help%2