0individual%20courtyards%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20explained%20that%20he%20planted%20the%20shrubs%20to%20attract%20butterflies%20and%20birds%2C%20and%20to%20diversify%20and%20improve%20the%20natural%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20traditional%20rainwater%20harvesting%20technique%20known%20as%20Khambhati%20Kuva%20(Percolation%20well)%20was%20implemented.%20The%20well%2C%20with%20a%20diameter%20of%2010%20feet%20and%20a%20depth%20of%2030%20feet%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20collect%20rainwater%20and%20recharge%20the%20ground.%20This%20well%20can%20absorb%2045%2C000%20to%2060%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20in%20just%20one%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20and%20running%20since%202021%2C%20Anand%20says%20looking%20back%20at%20his%20work%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20professional%2C%20I%20approach%20all%20projects%20with%20the%20same%20intensity.%20However%2C%20working%20on%20this%20project%20was%20unique.%20In%20our%20architectural%20education%2C%20we%20had%20never%20delved%20into%20questions%20about%20users%20to%20this%20extent.%20It%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20realisation%20that%20in%20designing%20any%20building%2C%20be%20it%20public%20structures%20or%20entire%20cities%2C%20we%20must%20consider%20a%20diverse%20set%20of%20users%2C%20ensuring%20that%20none%20are%20excluded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lesson%20of%20inclusivity%20that%20I%20learned%20from%20this%20experience%20has%20profoundly%20influenced%20my%20approach%20to%20new%20projects%2C%20where%20I%20strive%20to%20incorporate%20the%20valuable%20insights%20gained%20from%20the%20school%20project.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(All%20image%20credit%3A%20SEAlabs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706624472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%